name: CryptoReciclagem vol 1
description:
CryptoReciclagem vol 1 is a collection of new music from DJ and Music Producer Re-Surge. All songs were produced by him during the pandemic. 
The collection takes you for a tour in different nuances of the Brazilian northeast.

If you buy the collection you can send me a message
via twitter @re_surgee to request the wav track.

Cover art: Projeto Ciberdelia (@matheusfxavier)
